  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>LogTargetFile</TypeRef> constructor creates a file target with no file open and a flush filter of <TypeRef>SeverityFilter::WarningOrHigher</TypeRef>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[LogTargetFile();]]></Code>
  </Section>
